Goals
------
  - To make managing my music collection easier
  - Central location of all music
    - Samba share on /Storage/Music
    - Make sure that Katies music is included
    - Backup on Katie's extrernal hard drive.
    - Replace ~/Music with the Music share 
      - Make sure that it's write accessable
    - Mount Music on all computers
  - Verify that Itunes don't need to have uquic configuration options per machine.


